<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>lk ạ̉hdy yạ ạ̹lhy</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 lk ạ̉hdy yạ ạ̹lhy kl sẖkr mn fw̉ạdy
 wsẖfạhy tsẖdw ḥmdk wbk yḥlw ạ̹nsẖạdy
 fy lqạk tsẖfy rwḥy ạ̉hdạ̉ bʿd ạrtʿạd
 bslạm ạ̉bqy̱ ḥty̱ lw ạ̉ḥạṭt by ạlạ̉ʿạdy
 rwḥ qdsk ʿzạỷy bl hdạy whw zạdy
 mʿk lạ ạ̉kẖsẖy̱ msyraⁿạ fy jbạl ạ̉w whạd
 qrbk mny ygẖnyny mʿk yạ nbʿ ạlwdạd
 wklạmk lḥlqy ạ̉ḥly̱ mn qṭr ạlsẖhạd
 fṣlạty rby ạ̉srʿ sẖwqy lk bạzdyạd
 wạ̹ly̱ ạ̉n tạ̉ty rby ạjʿlny dwmaⁿạ fy ạstʿdạd</lyrics>
<hymn_number>6231</hymn_number>
<author>sʿạd mktby, dạnyạl ạlḥạj</author>
</song>